<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA9">
<l>porukkōṭṭō rēṉamāyp pukkiṭantāyk kaṉṟuṉ</l>
<l>ṉorukōṭṭiṉ mēṟkiṭanta taṉṟē – viritōṭṭa</l>
<l>cēvaṭiyai nīṭṭit ticainaṭuṅka viṇṭuḷaṅka</l>
<l>māvaṭivi ṉīyaḷanta maṇ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>That day she rested on one of your tusks, isn’t it, of you who entered as a boar</l>
<l>with fighting-tusks [and] rooted [it] up, the earth which you measured</l>
<l>in huge form, extending your feet red [like] broad-leaved [lotuses]</l>
<l>so that the directions trembled, the sky swayed?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
